 2019, using my Fujifilm XT20 camera. It showcases the Railway Administration Building in Kuala Lumpur, also known as Keretapi Tanah Melayu Berhad (KTMB). To learn more about this building, you can visit its [official website](https://www.ktmb.com.my/).\n\nFor additional details about the Railway Administration Building, refer to the References section below.\n\n## References\n\n1. Railway Administration Building in Kuala Lumpur, [Malaysia Trains](https://malaysiatrains.com/railway-administration-building-in-kuala-lumpur/)\n2. Gedung Ibu Pejabat Stasiun Kereta Api Tanah Melayu, [Wikipedia](https://id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Gedung_Ibu_Pejabat_Stasiun_Kereta_Api_Tanah_Melayu&oldid=23924685)\n3. KTMB Keretapi Tanah Melayu Berhad, [Google Maps](https://maps.app.goo.gl/86AnQT5uwqYoGSux8)\n","tableOfContents":{"items":[{"url":"#introduction","title":"Introduction"},{"url":"#about-the-featured-image","title":"About the Featured Image","items":[{"url":"#references","title":"References"}]}]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"a6fe62d7-164c-525f-a729-20b549bd7c72","frontmatter__p_type":"blog","frontmatter__slug":"my-first-post","__params":{"frontmatter__p_type":"blog","frontmatter__slug":"my-first-post"},"frontmatter":{"p_type":"blog","title":"My First Post","slug":"my-first-post","date":"2024-05-09","hero_img_src":"./figures/malaysia.jpg","hero_img_alt":"Railway Administration Building in Kuala Lumpur taken on January 31, 2019","keywords":[{"id":1,"name":"Architecture"},{"id":2,"name":"Photography"},{"id":3,"name":"Kuala Lumpur"}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["116989619","2484020538","3159585216","460926906"],"slicesMap":{}}